Package: detectXOR
Title: XOR Pattern Detection and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Jorn", family = "Lotsch",
                    role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "j.lotsch@em.uni-frankfurt.de",
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5818-6958")),
             person(given = "Alfred", family = "Ultsch",
                    role = "aut"))
Description: Provides comprehensive tools for detecting XOR-like patterns in
                        pairwise variable relationships within classification datasets. The package
                        implements tile-based pattern analysis, classwise Kendall tau correlations,
                        and group-wise Wilcoxon significance tests with parallel processing support
                        for large datasets. Includes advanced visualization capabilities for pattern
                        exploration and statistical validation.
